{"tid":1684102,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣南豐紗廠","createTime":"2019-10-31T02:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:25:26.000Z","uid":89349,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15a5cb16ebd9c1f6cf1c021585b02da1ea693836","tid":1684102,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJfTKQ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJfTKQ9.jpg&h=9da3685c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到呢一刻仲撐差佬果D，豬狗都不如。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家有冇帶過貓狗去荃灣南豐紗廠？<br />\n都幾好行wo, 有冷氣, 條路又夠闊, 狗仔行得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c15706152a2bf98fd6f43671098069d0900a5831","tid":1684102,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=9e031713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a1d1688aad8349394099a1680b246788c7107f","tid":1684102,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}